snippet.title: Boykisser Mayhem | A one-shot mod for friday night funkin' | FC (FLP + FLASH FILES)
snippet.description:
Hi! Welcome to this thing i made on my free time, cause, directing a mod and helping other mods!? Workload!? What is that? It's not like i have a bunch of stuff left to do. I got a bit lazy for the thumbnail and in-game icons cause i was a bit tired from doing stuff for this, and plus, it's a oneshot, not really a formal mod, so like, i can get lazy.

Anyway, i didn't plan this to get THIS a mod, this was something i did to practice vocals because i have zero idea of how to do them, but i ended up liking the song so much that i completed it and just made a one-shot mod for this, which explains why the chords and bass are exactly the same as bacon from katabooz, tho i did try to change at least some notes of the bass (i am so sorry lord katabooz i have sinned :(( i didn't mean to)

It was also my second time charting something, last time was with the innocence mod, which, god knows how long ago that was, but uh, it was quite the learning experience.

Anyway, just that, a simple one-shot i made for fun, flp is coming later as well as the flash files for it for those who would like to check that out, and that's it, cya!

I beg of u please check out katabooz, cause they have some really dope ass music, one of my inspirations (and i also stole from them for this song so please :skull:)

- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6JVOJDiY1FY&t=1s

Link to the mod: https://gamebanana.com/mods/462359

Link to the flp - https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1ooGj-jYru9ocyiAW1CRxp2zEdEJYvl18?usp=drive_link

The goofy chrom belongs to my friend ghostcat, please check them out!
-https://www.youtube.com/@GhostcatPNG/videos

Link to the flash anims - https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1ooGj-jYru9ocyiAW1CRxp2zEdEJYvl18?usp=drive_link

(ignore this stuff)

Friday Night Funkin' is an open-source donationware rhythm game first released in 2020 for a game jam. The game was developed by a team of four Newgrounds users, Cameron "Ninjamuffin99" Taylor, David "PhantomArcade" Brown, Isaac "Kawai Sprite" Garcia, and evilsk8r.

THESE FNF MODS ARE SO GOOD?! Like Garcello, Sonic.EXE, not StickyBM, Ruv, MidFight Masses, Hypno's Lullaby, Monochrome, Indie Cross, Undertale, Cuphead, Bendy, sans, Hotline 025, Pac Man, Hecker, Entity, Twinsomnia, DDLC, Monika, Freddy, Ourple Guy, FNAF at Freddy's, Markiplier, Geese, Zardy, Zardy B-Sides, Baldi's Basics, and more FNF Mods like that that are popular. I love playing all these mods and more like Imposter Among Us, D-Sides, Bat Man, Pibby, Neo, Fall Guys, MultiVersus, and other crazy worlds.
i love views, thank you for letting me steal uniquegeese and GhostcatPNG and now afurry again lol and now GhostcatPNG again lmaooo
#fnf #fnfmod #fridaynightfunkin #boykisser #thisishowyoulooksayingthatshit
